# nene2-js Rules

- Canonical docs: `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `docs/scope.md`, `docs/CONTRIBUTING.md`, `docs/workflow.md`, `docs/development/field-trials.md`.
- This repo is **TypeScript client ecosystem only** — not a Node port of NENE2, not nene-mcp.
- OpenAPI source of truth: NENE2 `docs/openapi/openapi.yaml`.
- Work from GitHub Issues; branch `type/issue-number-summary`; no direct commits to `main`.
- Conventional Commits: English type/scope, Japanese description, Issue number in subject.
- Do not commit secrets, `.env`, or `node_modules/`.
